": \"the \\u00a3250,000 mark\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1570}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was estimated to have earned a minimum of \\u00a339,000 for winning gold at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a minimum\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And now, with the 800m star in line to receive the coveted award - potentially becoming the fourth female winner in a row - it seems she is set to take up the mantle as the face of UK athletics and reap the financial benefits.\", \"from\": 1667, \"to\": 1893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1860, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK athletics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 800m star\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1702}, {\"ngram\": \"the coveted award\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1731}, {\"ngram\": \"the fourth female winner\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"a row\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"the mantle\", \"from\": 1822, \"to\": 1832}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1844}, {\"ngram\": \"the financial benefits\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1892}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, Hodgkinson wasn't even fully aware she had been nominated for the prize, as she toldStylist: \\\"It was actually my mum who told me [I'd been nominated] because I am in South Africa.\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 2079, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1900, \"end\": 1910, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.752573988136437, \"rank\": 0.3287730053974598, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q2